# Docs and ADR Standards

- Document decisions, not only conclusions.
- Include context, options considered, chosen option, and consequences.
- Keep docs actionable: add next steps and owner where possible.
- Update linked docs when behavior or architecture changes.

# ADR Template (short)

```md
## Context
## Decision
## Alternatives
## Consequences
```

# Rule of Thumb

- If a change affects system boundaries, write/update an ADR.
